3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper may discuss control and management of network traffic, which falls under this category. 
4. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper may touch upon security issues related to network traffic and topology. 
5. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper may discuss information theory concepts related to network traffic and topology.
